attributes.title: Don't Look Behind You! - Haunt Chaser
attributes.description: The Red Web Task Force joins Ky and Matt for their toughest investigation yet, in Haunt Chaser.

attributes.title: The Weirdest Dancing Quiz Game Ever - Papa's Quiz
attributes.description: Papa's Quiz is a really weird trivia game that involves adult Minions dancing. We may not know foreign leaders or history, but at least we know our Pokédex!

attributes.title: Shark Bites Make Me uWu - Raft - Part 1
attributes.description: Matt, Trevor, BK, and Alfredo set sail for a new adventure in Raft.

attributes.title: It's Familiar Yet So Different! - Rainbow Six Extraction
attributes.description:
Thanks to Ubisoft for sponsoring this video! Click here to buy now: https://ubi.li/Yqiot (ESRB: M)
Alfredo, Joe, and Trevor team up to save New York from an alien invasion, but who's going to save them?

attributes.title: Our Captain is a Shark Magnet - Raft Part 2
attributes.description: Matt, Trevor, BK, and Alfredo continue their adventure in Raft.

attributes.title: Our Randomizer Got Randomized - Super Mario 64 Randomizer
attributes.description: In Part 5 of our Super Mario 64 Randomizer, Matt and Michael wind up with even more rando than they planned for.

attributes.title: Dude, Where’s My Raft?! - Raft - Part 3
attributes.description: It’s part 3 of our raft adventure! This week, Matt learns a valuable lesson in Island permanence.

attributes.title: Cuphead AND Mugman Are Gonna Beat the Whole Game | Cuphead Part 1
attributes.description: Welcome to Cuphead Takeover Week! Alfredo "Al-cup-o" Diaz and Michael "Mug-chael" Jones are ready to tackle all of Cuphead (the video game) just in time for the release of Cuphead (the Cuphead Show television tele-show). Our boys have made a deal with the Devil, and now they must collect the souls of some very nasty bosses on their way to fighting the Devil himself. Come back every day at 12pm central to see the next episode, continuing until the game is finished.

attributes.title: Frustrations with the Flower Boss | Cuphead Part 2
attributes.description: Cuphead Takeover Week continues! In part 2, Michael and Alfredo become masters of the game, finally learning all the controls. Now that they can dash and use their specials, the game should be a walk in the park. attributes.description: Alfredo smells blood in the water. He's got a hankering for some magical shark.

attributes.description: It's Cuphead Takeover Week Part 3! Today, the boys work together to take down Beppi the Clown. It's very easy and they accomplish their goal very fast. attributes.description: It's Cuphead Takeover Week Part 4! Today, we fight a bird in a plane, jump around upside down, and then pound a dragon. Michael also learns a new technique to play optimally. attributes.description: It's Cuphead Takeover Week Part 5! Today, a new hero emerges, we catch a rat, a sweet queen gets soured, and we're finally on Island 3. attributes.description: It's Cuphead Takeover Week Part 6! Today, we handle the "water levels," with nautical-themed bosses and platforming. Why are water levels always the worst levels in the game? Also, an tried-and-true technique returns! In Cuphead Takeover Week, Alfredo "Al-cup-o" Diaz and Michael "Mug-chael" Jones are ready to tackle all of Cuphead (the video game) just in time for the release of Cuphead (the Cuphead Show television tele-show). Come back every day at 12pm central to see the next episode, continuing until the game is finished.

attributes.title: Can We Beat King Dice Before the Video Ends? | Cuphead Part 7
attributes.description: It's Cuphead Takeover Week Part 7! Michael and Alfredo take on the remaining bosses on Inkwell Isle 3 and then make their way into Inkwell Hell to take on the dastardly King Dice. King Dice is such a marathon of a boss, can the cup boys do it before the end of the video? In Cuphead Takeover Week, Alfredo "Al-cup-o" Diaz and Michael "Mug-chael" Jones are ready to tackle all of Cuphead (the video game) just in time for the release of Cuphead (the Cuphead Show television tele-show). Come back every day at 12pm central to see the next episode, continuing until the game is finished.

attributes.title: Cuphead Has a Bad Ending? | Cuphead Part 8 (FINALE)
attributes.description: It's the finale of Cuphead Takeover Week! Something went horribly wrong and now Al-cup-o and Mug-chael are back here again, ready to face off against the Devil. They also challenge themselves with some extra tough bosses. When will the pain end? In Cuphead Takeover Week, Alfredo "Al-cup-o" Diaz and Michael "Mug-chael" Jones are ready to tackle all of Cuphead (the video game) just in time for the release of Cuphead (the Cuphead Show television tele-show). Our boys have made a deal with the Devil, and now they must collect the souls of some very nasty bosses on their way to fighting the Devil himself. Stop coming back (for Cuphead - come back for our other great content). It's over. We're done. The pain is immense. We're not doing this again - at least not unitl the Delicious Last Course DLC releases.

attributes.title: Mysteries On The Ship Wreck - Raft - Part 5
attributes.description: It’s part 5 of our raft adventure! This week, the gang explores a shipwreck, upgrades their raft with an engine, and finally organize their storage.

attributes.title: Bowser's Randomized Kingdom - Super Mario 64 Randomizer
attributes.description: It's Part 6 of the Super Mario 64 Randomizer! Today, Matt makes Michael suffer through the last 7 stars in order to unlock the final fight with Bowser. Will we finally make it to the end of the randomizer?

attributes.title: Surviving an Island FULL OF BEARS! - Raft - Part 6
attributes.description: It's part 6 of our Raft adventure. Today, the gang starts an animal farm, questions their fondness for llamas, and finds a huge island that's filthy with bears.

attributes.title: Can Two ADULTS Beat Freddi Fish? - Friendly Fire
attributes.description: BK introduces Ky to her childhood games as they put on their detective hats and play through the entirety of Freddi Fish and The Case of The Stolen Conch Shell.

attributes.title: Ditching Your Friends in a Boss Battle - Raft - Part 7
attributes.description: Ditching Your Friends in a Boss Battle - Raft - Part 7	 It’s time for more Raft! This week, The gang goes up against the mother of all bears as they continue their search for civilization.

attributes.title: Everything is WRONG - Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer
attributes.description: It's the start of the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer and we're on our way to collecting 98 jiggies in order to beat Gruntilda. Wait...98 jiggies!?!?

attributes.title: Launching Rockets On The Biggest Island Yet - Raft - Part 8
attributes.description: It’s time for part 8 of our Raft adventure! The gang arrives at Caravan Island, where they discover ziplines, rockets, and llamas.

attributes.title: Bees Destroy Our Souls - Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer Part 2
attributes.description: We continue the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer as the bees and ghosts are never-ending in their quest to stop us from collecting 98 Jiggies.

attributes.title: We Found A Floating CITY - Raft - Part 9
attributes.description: It's Part 9 in our Raft adventure! The crew makes improves their raft and finds a mystery city!

attributes.title: We Create the WEIRDEST Custom Characters in WWE 2K22
attributes.description: In this gameplay, we take the character creator in WWE 2K22 to its limits as we wrestle with our new alter egos.

attributes.title: Will Overconfidence Be Our Downfall? - Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #3
attributes.description: We continue the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer and taunt our own luck as we try to patch together missing pieces and see how far we can get without flying.

attributes.title: Solving The Last Raft City Mystery - Raft - Part 10
attributes.description: It’s the final episode of our Raft adventure! This week, the gang tries to find civilization, rebuild society, and learn to play piano.

attributes.title: Trivial Pursuit Has a Sequel?! - Trivial Pursuit 2
attributes.description: It’s time for more Trivia! Join Jack, Michael, Alfredo, and Trevor as they compete to prove who the smartest person in the room truly is.

attributes.title: We're Gonna Beat FNAF Security Breach! | Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach (Part 1)
attributes.description: Alfredo and Trevor bring their Red Web skills to the Pizzaplex as we begin our journey through the entirety of Five Nights at Freddy's: Security Breach! Why is Freddy so friendly? Surely this is a trap, right? Also, Chica is sexy, and I won't hear otherwise.

attributes.title: How Many More Things Can We Break?! - Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #4
attributes.description: The Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer keeps going as more and more things break down, our hearts included.

attributes.title: Chica Has a Crush On Me?! | Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach ( Part 2)
attributes.description: Alfredo and Trevor are back at it for part 2 in Friday Night at Freddy’s: Security Breach! We’ve got cups of water being spilled, we’ve got pizza being made, we’ve got maps being forcefully handed to us, we’ve got Freddy being our friend. And yeah, we’ve got Chica still being sexy…and hella spooky.

attributes.title: There Are No Check Points?! | Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach (Part 3)
attributes.description: Alfredo and Trevor are at it again for part 3 in Friday Night at Freddy’s: Security Breach! Spooky chaos ensues as they travel to new parts of the Pizzaplex to try and escape the terrifying clutches of Montgomery Croc and Roxanne Wolf near the Main Stage. Will Trevor’s elevator dance party bring them good luck and can Alfredo’s yells inspire them?

attributes.title: Animatronics Without Their Skin Are FREAKY! | Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach (Part 4)
attributes.description: Alfredo and Trevor are back for more spooks in Friday Night at Freddy’s: Security Breach! You're in for a treat with this one. Endoskeleton’s GALORE, so brace yourself to keep looking back. Freddy seems to be in trouble, is he okay? Is it super toasty in the room Alfredo and Trevor are playing in? The answer is yes. It’s real toasty. Plus, we get a visit from the Baba Yaga throughout all of this scary chaos. How grand!

attributes.title: We BREAK UP With Chica | Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach (Part 5)
attributes.description: It’s part 5 of Trevor and Alfredo’s trip through Five Nights at Freddy's: Security Breach. This time, they take on some security bots in Fazer Blast, unravel more of the mysteries within the Pizzaplex, and finally break up with Chica.. She does not take it well.

attributes.title: Everything Is Scarier In The Trash! | Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach (Part 6)
attributes.description: Trevor and Alfredo are back with part 6 of their FNAF adventure! They’ve been sent to the trash by Chica, but if they can survive and upgrade Freddy, They’re one step closer to escaping the Pizzaplex.

attributes.title: Let's Play Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #5 - Mummies Suck
attributes.description: We start narrowing down the worlds as we continue our way through the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer.

attributes.title: The Walking Dead VR Is TOO REAL
attributes.description: A zombie apocalypse has taken over the virtual world and there’s only one person tough enough to take them on.. But we got Trevor instead. With Alfredo, Joe, and Matt watching his back, the gang takes on the zombie-filled streets of The Walking Dead: Saints and Sinners.

attributes.title: Hitman VR is the GREATEST Game!
attributes.description: When the virtual world is in need of some saving. There's only one group to call... Achievement Hunter? That's right! We take the dive into Hitman VR! Guided by Gavin, our Master Assassin, Alfredo, Michael, and Jack come along on the first virtual chaos-filled Hitman mission.

attributes.title: Can We Make It to the Ending of Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach? (Part 7 FINALE)
attributes.description: It’s time! Part 7 and the FINALE of Alfredo and Trevor playing Five Night’s at Freddy’s: Security Breach! Join them as they’re make their way on through the Pizzaplex for the final time, all while escaping the clutches of the DJ Music Man and Chica, and Monty. Which of the 6 endings will we get at the end? Well, you’ll just have to watch and see.

attributes.title: Let's Play Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #6 - Using the Last of Our Sanity
attributes.description: It's time for the last semi-decent level in the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer as we get closer to collecting all the jiggies.

attributes.title: Let's Play Rubber Bandits - Gang Beasts Meets Heisting
attributes.description: The time for heisting and beating each other down is here as Matt, Joe, Lindsay, and Ky play Rubber Bandits.

attributes.title: Let's Play Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #7 - This Level is HELL
attributes.description: We run into plenty of pain as the time has finally come to tackle Rusty Bucket Bay in the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer.

attributes.title: Let’s Play VR After the Fall | Co-Op Zombie Mayhem
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter is left out in the cold and must fend for themselves against the zombie hoard. Alfredo, Michael, Gavin, and Jeremy play through the first level of After the Fall. Time to find out who's a baby and who's a big kid! (at least when it comes to reloading)

attributes.title: Let's Play Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #8 - Can We Collect Every Note in Rusty Bucket Bay?
attributes.description: The pain of Rusty Bucket Bay continues as we see how many notes we can get before dying or losing our minds in the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer.

attributes.title: Let’s Play Nintendo Switch Sports Bowling
attributes.description: Nintendo Switch Sports is here, so now we’re here to see who the best at bowling in the virtual world is. Will Michael, Matt, Ky, and Alfredo get a turkey? Test out the “granny” style in game? Yeah, most definitely on that latter one.

attributes.title: Let's Play Poppy Playtime Chapter 2 | We're back!
attributes.description: Alfredo and Trevor are back for Poppy Playtime Chapter 2!  The two find themselves playing new games and solving new puzzles one sticky hand at a time.

attributes.title: Let's Play Poppy Playtime Chapter 2 Part 2 | The Final Games
attributes.description: In the last episode, Alfredo and Trevor managed to slap, jump, and run part way through chapter 2 of Poppy Playtime.  Now they look to get the remaining codes needed for the train as they face their toughest challenge yet, the dark.

attributes.title: Let's Play Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #9 - Click Clock Chaos
attributes.description: We make our way into Click Clock Wood and four seasons means four times the randomization in the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer.

attributes.title: Let’s Play VR Mini Golf | Golf Fore Dummies
attributes.description: It’s time for more Walkabout Mini Golf VR! Michael, Trevor, Gavin, and Joe take some much needed time off and head to the virtual beach for some mini golf, secret ball hunting, and shoving golf clubs into each other's heads… The perfect vacation.

attributes.title: Let's Play Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #10 - The Final Jiggie
attributes.description: We chase after the final jiggies in the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer as we finish traversing the four seasons of Click Clock Wood.

attributes.title: Let's Play Nintendo Switch Sports Tennis - Fatigue is Key!
attributes.description: Another Nintendo Switch Sports matchup is here with Alfredo and Ky versus Michael and BK in tennis! Intensity. Drama. Fatigue. It's all here for you to witness in all of its sweaty glory.

attributes.title: Let's Play Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer #11 - The Final Boss
attributes.description: The finale of the Banjo-Kazooie Randomizer is upon us! With 98 jiggies, 877 notes, and our pride at stake, can we defeat Grunty and save Tooty?

attributes.title: STAR WARS in VR - Blade & Sorcery (The Outer Rim)
attributes.description: To satisfy our need to become intergalactic space fighters, Trevor, Alfredo, and the Chosen One, BK, take on the evil Emperor, Michael, in an epic fight in Star Wars Blade & Sorcery!

attributes.title: Let's Play Volleyball in Nintendo Switch Sports!
attributes.description: Coming fresh off the tennis court, Michael and Ky team up to take on Matt and Lindsay in two sets of high paced Nintendo Switch Sports Volleyball.  They will need to set, spike, and, scream to come out victorious in today's Let's Play.

attributes.title: Let’s Play Among Us with Distractions! | State Farm Gamerhood
attributes.description:
Michael, BK, Alfredo and Jeremy join streamers Berleezy, Im Dontai, Sypherpk, and Emme Montogomery in a game of Among Us. Whoever wins gets a prize for charity and Jake from State Farm's heart. 
Thanks to State Farm for sponsoring this video. Check out the State Farm Gamerhood Challenge at 5 PM ET on Wednesdays on the following channels http://twitch.tv/statefarm | http://roosterteeth.com/live | http://youtube.com/roosterteeth | http://twitch.tv/roosterteeth

attributes.title: Let's Play Wheel of Fortune: Trivia Games Are Back!
attributes.description: Everyone's favorite game show is back as Matt, BK, and Ky battle it out in Wheel of Fortune!

attributes.title: Let's Play Baby Hands VR: Don't Eat the Crayons!
attributes.description: From eating crayons, flooding bathrooms, and racing track cars, join Joe as he looks to recapture his youth as a baby under the supervision of dads Michael and Alfredo in Baby Hands VR!

attributes.title: Let's Play Brawlhalla Team House VS Team Van | State Farm #Gamerhood
attributes.description:
Michael, BK, Alfredo and Jeremy join streamers Berleezy, Im Dontai, Sypherpk, and Emme Montogomery in a game of Brawlhalla. It's team tiny house vs team van and the winner gets Jake from State Farm's heart!
Thanks to State Farm for sponsoring this video. Check out the State Farm Gamerhood Challenge at 5 PM ET on Wednesdays on the following channels http://twitch.tv/statefarm | http://roosterteeth.com/live | http://youtube.com/roosterteeth | http://twitch.tv/roosterteeth

attributes.title: Let’s Play Midnight Ghost Hunt: Prop Hunt + Ghost Busters
attributes.description: Having ghost problems?  You probably shouldn't call Achievement Hunter, but if you do Michael, Lindsay, Alfredo, Matt, Ky, and Joe will be there!  The gang shows off their robust ghost hunting skills, weapons, and teamwork as the ghosts attempt to fight back in this Gmod Prop Hunt inspired game "Midnight Ghost Hunt".

attributes.title: Fighting Zombies in VR | Let's Play Propagation VR
attributes.description: Alfredo and Joe are playing Propagation VR where they have to hold their ground as they fight off waves of zombies, spiders, and all sorts of baddies, as well as some Achievement Hunters who are messing with them IRL.

attributes.title: Let's Play No Man's Sky - We Land On Planet Throbbing Sack
attributes.description: We're starting from the beginning and playing No Man's Sky with Gavin, Trevor, BK, and Matt. We'll be with them as they traverse through space, a hot and hellish throbbing sack of a planet, and encounter some of thee ugliest and most interesting creatures we've ever seen as they try to repair their ship and build a base of operations before venturing out into the unknowns of space!

attributes.title: The Quarry Full Playthrough Part 1: Better Than Until Dawn?
attributes.description: We begin our angsty horror adventure as we playthrough the entire story of The Quarry. Every day this week, we'll be releasing another part until we finish this game, one way or another. Camp has just ended, and the young Counselors need to pack up and leave before nightfall. How hard could it be?

attributes.title: Let’s Play Arcadeggedon - Bringin’ Down THE MAN
attributes.description:
Thanks to IllFonic for sponsoring this video. Check out Arcadegeddon here: www.Arcadegeddon.com.
Alfredo, Matt, Ky, and Joe fight off robot hordes to save their uncle’s arcade in Arcadeggedon. The CEO doesn’t stand a chance against their rockets, lobbers, and bats!

attributes.title: The Quarry Full Playthrough Part 2: Why Fredo Why!
attributes.description: We continue our angsty horror adventure as we playthrough the entire story of The Quarry. Every day this week, we'll be releasing another part until we finish this game, one way or another. The couples must deal with the fallout of the scandalous kiss, while a monster and monsterous hunter tracks them down. Who gets to keep the guns? What will happen to Emma when she's alone? How many tarot cards will Alfredo miss? Let's choose our path.

attributes.title: The Quarry Full Playthrough Part 3: That's a LOT of Blood
attributes.description: We're back with Chapters 5 and 6 of The Quarry! Every day this week, we'll be releasing another part until we finish this game, one way or another. Today, we make lots of decisions concerning out shotgun, we make a VERY bloody choice, and someone is spooked right out of their skin.

attributes.title: The Quarry Full Playthrough Part 4: An Eye For an Eye
attributes.description: We're back with Chapters 7 and 8 of The Quarry! Every day this week, we'll be releasing another part until we finish this game, one way or another.  Today, the gang will need to keep their EYE on the prize if they want to solve the mystery and escape in one piece.

attributes.title: The Quarry Full Playthrough Finale: How Did It End This Way?
attributes.description: It's the finale of The Quarry as we take on chapter's 9 and 10! Today, we are jump scared by ourselves, question every decision we've possibly made this game, and maybe just maybe finally learn the characters names and get some counselors through the night.

attributes.title: If Duck Hunt was a VR HORROR Game - Let's Play Duck Season
attributes.description: Ky is playing Duck Season, a VR shooting game that feels a lot like Duck Hunt on Nintendo...only...something is very, very wrong. Matt, Trevor, and BK join her on the couch as they watch her go through this completely normal, not spooky video game.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer | Full Zelda Playthrough with Items Out of Order! - Pt. 1
attributes.description: In this new Randomizer, Michael and Matt play The Legend of Zelda: The Wind Waker with our new heroine Glink! What will Michael and Matt experience in this new journey! Hilarity ensues...

attributes.title: Being a Wizard in VR SUCKS | Let's Play Magic Realm Online
attributes.description: We hop into VR to learn how to be Wizards, Archers, and Gunslingers in Magic Realm Online.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer | Full Zelda Playthrough with Items Out of Order! - Pt. 2
attributes.description: Here we are again, following our ""fairly old"" maiden Glink! I wonder if she will ever get her hands on the Master Sword?! She does, however, make a pit stop with a game of KA-BOOM and SPLOOSH!

attributes.title: Let's Play: Fall Guys Sweet Thieves!
attributes.description:
Bonus Rounds Start at: 28:30

Michael, Ky, Matt, and A Large Turtle (Trevor) try to defend and steal as many candies as possible in the ""Sweet Thieves"" limited time mode in Fall Guys!

attributes.title: Let's Play Overwatch 2 Beta: Clash at Colosseo!
attributes.description: Overwatch is back! Trevor, Matt, BK, Joe, and Alfredo hop into the beta and test out new heroes, maps, and modes. Let’s see if they stand a chance against the new Junker Queen.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, but we CAN’T FIND A SWORD! - Pt. 3
attributes.description: We find ourselves today following Glink throughout the lands. We finally found the grappling hook, which is something that is very useful for us! Let us use this new found item to discover new chests and... maybe get the Master Sword?

attributes.title: Let's Play No Man's Sky - Building Our Base on Throbbing Sack
attributes.description: We're back in No Man's Sky and it's time to build our base on Throbbing Sack! Luckily Gavin, Trevor, BK, and Matt are very talented at building and showcase their skills at constructing a safe, secure, homey base. Can they get off the planet and get to the space station safely and soundly with zero issues? I think you already know the answer to that.

attributes.title: Raft Got an UPDATE! - Part 11
attributes.description: Raft is back! The gang sets sail again as they discover new locations, enemies, and story in Raft’s Final Chapter update.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer | Full Zelda Playthrough with Items Out of Order! - Pt. 4
attributes.description: We have traveled across the land in search of chests, and have failed at finding a weapon that we could use. At least, that is what we would have said until now! Watch us, as we tackle the ghost ship!

attributes.title: Bar Fighting in VR - Let’s Play Drunkn Bar Fight
attributes.description: It’s VR time! This week, Alfredo and Trevor show Michael around Drunkn Bar Fight. Let’s see if anyone can survive Michael’s trip to the bar, supermarket, jail, and even a wedding!

attributes.title: Let's Play: MultiVersus - Justice League Vs. Mystery Inc.
attributes.description: Enter the multiverse with Matt, BK, Joe, and Alfredo as they battle it out with Warner Brother properties in the new game "MultiVersus"!

attributes.title: We Take On The MEGALODON! - Raft - Part 12
attributes.description: It’s time for more Raft! The Crew explores the flooded skyscrapers and finds what’s been causing all that rumbling. We’ll see how our favorite Shark Mage fairs against his toughest foe yet, the Mega Shark.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer | Full Zelda Playthrough with Items Out of Order! - Pt. 5
attributes.description: We're back with Michael and Matt sailing throughout the sea looking for items of value! I wonder if Matt will continue to be a thorn in Michael's shoe? I guess there is only one way to find out. Tune in as Matt ruffles Michael's feathers once again!

attributes.title: Let's Play Mario Strikers: Battle League | Kicking and Screaming and More Screaming
attributes.description: This week Matt, BK, Alfredo, and Joe are playing Mario Strikers: Battle League! They're taking on the Muscle Cup as a team, but can they coordinate and win as a team? More importantly, can they all agree if Daisy is a redhead or a brunette AND remember the name of the game they're playing?

attributes.title: There's a New Snow Island in Raft! - Raft Update - Part 13
attributes.description: It's Raft time, Rafties! The Crew delves into the new snowy island, Temperance, explores a deserted village, fights off polar bears, and discovers a big secret on the island!

attributes.title: Fighting the Zombie Apocalypse in VR | Let's Play Arizona Sunshine
attributes.description: Alfredo and Joe are playing some VR in Arizona Sunshine this week! Surviving the zombie apocalypse is the name of the game here. Luckily, Alfredo and Joe have each other's backs. And by backs, I mean a grenade in their face, so buckle the hell in.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, Glink and the Battle of the Wizzrobes! - Pt. 6
attributes.description: After the canon game time waster that Matt orchestrated, they continue their search going after Octos and clearing platforms. Michael encounters some pesky Wizzrobes that challenge his sanity. Can Glink defeat these diabolical wizzrobes? Let us find out!

attributes.title: We Make it To UTOPIA - Raft Update - Part 14
attributes.description: Our Rafters have finally Rafted to Utopia! Join them as they travel to this "perfect" area, discuss being shy poopers, solve some puzzles, maybe even redecorate a thing or two on the raft, and more! Let's Raft it up, my Raftonians.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, WE FOUND THE TINGLE STATUES! - Pt. 7
attributes.description: We start our Journey today by sailing into the Tower of the Gods! What treasures will we find inside, and what challenges await us? We also found all of the Tingle statues! Will Tingle reward Michael with a sword, or will it only be more rupees? Myatt, tell your friend we want a sword!

attributes.title: Let's Play No Man's Sky - Our First Hyperdrive! (#3)
attributes.description: It's time to build our hyperdrives and the get the heck outta this galaxy! We'll discover new planets, new creatures, and new things about ourselves. Like, does Gavin remember to pack enough fuel on his ship before going into space? Let's find out together, my fellow No Man's Skytonians.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, IT'S HAMMER TIME! - Pt. 8
attributes.description: The time has finally come! After brutal battles with rats and wizzrobes, Glink has finally done it! With Glink's little sister's soup, and with aching bones, she has obtained the SKULL HAMMER!

attributes.title: Let's Play Minecraft in VR | This is AWESOME!
attributes.description: Minecraft is back, but this time we are in VR!  Join Matt, Michael, Jack, and Alfredo as they farm, mine, and make some new pet friends all inside of Virtual Reality.

attributes.title: Can Joe Stop Matt From Achieving "Infallible" in Fall Guys?
attributes.description: "Infallible" [ in-fal-uh-buhl ] "Unfailing in effectiveness or operation; certain."  To achieve said infallibility, Matt will have to win 5 games in a row in Fall Guy alongside Michael, Lindsay, and Joe who is determined to stop him right at the finish line.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, 10,000 Rupees When All You Need is a Sword! - Pt. 9
attributes.description: How many checks need to be checked to find a proper weapon? We did, however, get the skull hammer to make destroying the ChuChus that much easier! With all of these lost rupees and treasure charts, we are bound to get something good... Right?

attributes.title: Let's Play Loco Dojo - What if Mario Party Was in VR?
attributes.description: What if Mario Party was in VR and you had to spray your friends with some chum to get sharks to attack them, or milk some cows and gather milk as fast as you can, or smash ants before they steal you food? Well that's exactly what Alfredo, Michael, Trevor, and Joe are doing in Loco Dojo in VR! Let's go watch them not do any kind of gestures that would be questionable at best.

attributes.title: Let's Play No Man's Sky - We're Lost in Space! (#4)
attributes.description: While the gang tries to get Gavin to the right system, their quest through the galaxy continues! New planets are explored, beasts are tamed, and space pirates are fought in this episode of No Man’s Sky!

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, GRANNY IS ITCHING FOR A FIGHT! - Pt. 10
attributes.description: After finding the hammer and a sword, things are really starting to move! With so many more checks opening up, its time for granny to raise her sail and set forth out to sea once again!

attributes.title: Let's Play Return to Rapture - A Half Life: Alyx Bioshock VR Mod!
attributes.description: We're DIVING, yeah I said it, into a real unique Half Life: Alyx mod that brings the world of Rapture and Bioshock into VR. Our good man Alfredo is going to brave the deep depths of the ocean for us all, but he's not alone, he's got Michael and BK on the couch as they coach and commentate on his efforts. Would you kindly join us for the journey?

attributes.title: The ENDING OF Raft! - Raft Update - Part 15 (Finale)
attributes.description: It’s the final episode of Raft! As our adventure comes to a close, the gang discovers the final mysteries of Utopia and what dangers have been waiting for our Rafters.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, A GRANNY GLINK GLOW UP!? - Pt. 11
attributes.description: We're back with another chapter of "The Legend of Glink"! Glink has been through a lot lately. After all the fighting she has done, and all the hits she has taken, when will it finally be her time to face Ganon? When will she finally be able to rest her aching bones?

attributes.title: How I beat my first Dark Souls | The Birth Of Majin Joe
attributes.description: Having never played a Dark Souls game, Majin Joe will be taken under Michaels wing in an attempt to restore the ember and embrace the darkness of Dark Souls III.  Will Michael be able to guide Majin Joe through the Kingdom of Lothric or will his flame burn out before the first bell is rung?

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, GRANNY COMES HOME! - Pt. 12
attributes.description: It has been awhile since Glink visited her little sister. There are so many stories Glink wants to tell her sister about! I hope they can talk about it over a fresh batch of soup! Glink can't stay too long though. She still has a score to settle with Ganon!

attributes.title: Team RWBY Plays Beat Saber to Vol. 1 Music | Let's Play BEAT SABER
attributes.description: In celebration of RWBY: Ice Queendom airing, Lindsay (Ruby) and Barbara (Yang) play some of the music from the show in BEAT SABER!  Watch the RWBY: Ice Queendom English Dub premiere now! https://roosterteeth.com/watch/rwby-ice-queendom-season-1-dub-rwby-ice-queendom  Don't know what RWBY: Ice Queendom is? Check out the trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0UFyKiN24mY

attributes.title: Let's Play No Man's Sky - Touring WEIRD Planets (#5)
attributes.description: It’s time for more No Man’s Sky! This week, Trevor shows everyone the new planet he discovered, a lot of pirate fights happen, and everyone tries their best to not get distracted by side quests.

attributes.title: Let's Play Halo 5: LASO - F*CK!
attributes.description: LASO ALARM! It is time to tackle Halo 5 with ALL the skulls on. I'll tell you right now that this will suck for our players, but that provides PLENTY of good content for us. Gavin, Alfredo, Michael, and Joe will make their way through level 1 of the Halo 5 campaign, but will their spirits be crushed and want to quit playing? Oh, absolutely, but that's too bad because this is LASO.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, GLINK, THE ONE TRUE HERO! - Pt. 13
attributes.description: After obtaining the FULLY POWERED master sword, Glink is one step closer towards defeating the evil Ganon. There are still a couple things that she needs in order to fight Ganon. I wonder how long it will take to find them?

attributes.title: Trapped in VR With Puppets That Want To Kill Us
attributes.description: It's October! That means time to scare the pants off ourselves with some VR horror games! We're starting with a puppet-themed horror game that is part stealth, part puzzles, all puppet! It's Hello Puppets!

attributes.title: The True Dark Souls Starts Here - My First Souls Game #2
attributes.description: It's back to Dark Souls 3 for first timer Joe and souls veteran Michael.  After defeating the crystal lizard and Iudex Gundry, Majin Joe now faces The High Wall of Lothric.  Majin Joe will have to deal with shield knight, little men, a dragon, ladders, and a not boss in order to reach the next boss fight.  Will he be able to do it?  Or will he succumb to the pressure of Dark Souls?

attributes.title: LASO the Movie - Let’s Play Halo 5 LASO #2
attributes.description: I hope you're all ready. Halo 5: LASO The Movie is here in all of it's glory. You thought the extended edition of Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers was long? Well, buckle the fuck in because we are about to watch our boys struggle, cry (on the inside and outside a little bit), scream, swear, sweat, serenade briefly, and work together for several hours through level 2 of Halo 5 LASO.

attributes.title: Wind Waker Randomizer, THE IMMORTAL GRANNY! - Pt. 14
attributes.description: Glink has proven herself to be one of the best warriors out there to date, maybe even better than the hero of time himself! Ganon has to be shaking in his boots right now in anticipation of the one true hero, Glink!

attributes.title: Running and Screaming in a Haunted VR House
attributes.description: Scary VR continues as we subject Joe to being chased around by ghosts in Home Sweet Home VR! But honestly, he might be more afraid of doors than the ghosts.

attributes.title: Let's Play No Man's Sky - The Search For Gavin (#6)
attributes.description: It’s No Man’s Sky time! This week, we catch up with Artemis, make some new friends at the space station, Trevor shows what a good space mayor he is, and we find out if Gavin really exists.

attributes.title: Hell Continues, We're STILL on Level 2 - Let's Play Halo 5 LASO (#3)
attributes.description: In a series of unfortunate sticky grenades, it's time to return to Level 2. Thanks, Gavin's Xbox. So get ready (again) for level 2 of Halo 5 LASO! Will their strategies be better? Will there be less tears? Will they beat the damn thing? Only one way to find out...

attributes.title: Whisper! Or The Monster Will KILL US | Escape the Ayuwoki
attributes.description: The Halloween season is upon us as Achievement Hunter plays through Escape the Ayuwoki! Join Jack, Joe, and Lindsay as they hide in conspicuous places, sacrifice rats, and taunt the vicious monster chasing them.

attributes.title: Control Jump Scares in Horror VR | Let’s Play Reiko’s Fragments
attributes.description: It’s time for more scary VR! This week, Alfredo and Joe try to escape a haunted house in Reiko's Fragments, while Trevor and Michael do everything they can to stop them. You know what they say: when one door closes, an evil spirit will find you.

attributes.title: Ultimate Chicken Horse - The Lost Summer Levels!
attributes.description: This past summer, we sat down for some fun in the sun to see who comes out as the Ultimate Chicken Horse.

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 1
attributes.description: YDYD returns in 7 Days to Die! This season, we have 7 Days to make enough gyrocopters for each surviving team member to escape our apocalyptic confines. But we only get one life each! Because when Ya Dead, Ya Dead.

attributes.title: Let's Play The Mortuary Assistant (Full Game)
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter takes on the disturbing horror game of The Mortuary Assistant as they take care of dead bodies, search for demonic symbols, and try to survive their unescapable shift.

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 2
attributes.description: It's day 2 of Ya Dead Ya Dead in 7 Days to Die.  After traveling to our new home base of operations, it's time to take on new tasks, make new food, and fight an unexpected zombie horde.

attributes.title: Majin Joe Vs. The Big Lady | My First Dark Souls Game #3
attributes.description: Majin Joe continues his quest along the High Wall of Lothric as he ventures into the chamber of Vordt of the Boreal Valley.  Vordt wont be Majin Joe's only test though.  If he can defeat the four legged frozen beast, what lies ahead may fair much tougher than the pink guy may have expected.

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 3
attributes.description: Day 3 of surviving the zombie apocalypse is here! Ya Dead Ya Dead is ready for you to witness the highs and the 'oh-so-goddamn' lows. Can they even make it through another day? Will there be lots of sillies and scaries? How about Ya Watch Ya Watch and find out?

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 4
attributes.description: It’s Day 4 of Ya Dead Ya Dead!  As Day 7 draws closer, the gang focuses on leveling up and gathering resources to prepare. But it’s a big world, maybe they aren’t the only survivors out there..

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 5
attributes.description: We want to ride our bicycles, we want to ride our bikes! It's Day 5 and we discover other survivors are lurking in the shadows. Maybe they can help us build our gyrocopters? Or at least some bikes?

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 6
attributes.description: Goodness gracious, we're so close to zombie-horde night in 7 Days to Die! It's Ya Dead Ya Dead, and we hope you feast on this episode as the team preps for the Blood Moon. Can they make it through another day to thrive and survive? It's like Gandalf once said to Frodo, "you're just gonna have to watch the episode and find out, you son of a gun." I love that scene.

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 7
attributes.description: It's the 7th day in Ya Dead Ya Dead, which means it’s time for the 7th Night! Time to see if all those preparations were enough to keep out the horde, or if anyone will be left to make those gyrocopters.

attributes.title: LASO: The Musical - Let's Play Halo 5 LASO (#4)
attributes.description: LASO ALARM! Part 4 is here and yes, you're seeing that timecode correctly. Our lads have brought along a few of their classic hits to sing themselves (and us) through this monster of a level. Tanks, Knights, and Dogs are plenty abound. I'd recommend a snack or seven, getting real comfy, and hunkering down for the chaos that is Halo 5 LASO.

attributes.title: The Legend of The Sack Slayer | My First Dark Souls Game #4
attributes.description: Here we are, back in Dark Souls 3 with the newbie and the veteran! As we continue through the game, he encounters rats, pot boys, and sacks that need to be slayed. Will Majin Joe prevail, or will he suffer "multiple" painful deaths?

attributes.title: Let’s Play 7 Days to Die with PERMADEATH! - Day 8 (Epilogue)
attributes.description: We survived the 7th night! Now we just have to build the gyrocopters and not put ourselves in danger. How hard can it be?

attributes.title: God of War Ragnarök - Part 1
attributes.description: It's the start of God of War Week! Michotos (yes you read that right) and his son Joetreus start their epic adventure RIGHT NOW! Join our crew for an entire WEEK of blood, sweat, and tears as they get started in God of War Ragnarök.

attributes.title: This VR Sandbox is a GAMECHANGER
attributes.description: The possibilities for madness are endless in Bonelab VR! Trevor takes the reigns of VR, guided by Alfredo and Michael as he beats down enemies with guns and computer monitors, uses a weapon gacha system, and tries out some Big Bone Bowling!

attributes.title: God of War Ragnarök - Part 2
attributes.description: It’s the second day of God of War Week!  After fighting off Bear-treus, the gang dusts off their Blades of Chaos, unlock some new abilities, and do some father son bonding during Fimbulwinter.

attributes.title: God of War Ragnarök - Part 3
attributes.description: God of War week continues! Alfredýr joins Michotos and Joetreus on the couch for part 3. We've got more bonding, more admiration for the prettiness of the game, and some good ol' fashion boat traveling.

attributes.title: God of War Ragnarök - Part 4
attributes.description: We're back and it's more God of War Ragnarök for you all! Michotos, Joetreus, and Alfredýr keep on keeping on as they journey to Svartalfheim and press on in trying to find Týr. More monsters, more boating, more banter coming your way. God (of War) speed, friends!

attributes.title: God of War Ragnarök - Part 5
attributes.description: Tis' the end of God of War week! Michotos, Joetreus, and Alfredýr truly bring their best as they continue their search for Týr, take on the most powerful foes yet, and get into an abundance of familial drama.

attributes.title: Choose our next series! Game 1: Grounded
attributes.description: Welcome to Pilot Week: Choose Your Own Let's Play. To learn more, turn to below the description. |  Join BK, Matt, Jack, and Trevor as they navigate the backyard in an attempt to return to normal size and escape the dangers that await them! | Choose Your Own Let's Play in Pilot Week! Over five days, Achievement Hunter will be releasing the first video in five potential series we're very excited to play. Choose which video you want to see more of with your views. Whichever video winds up with the most views will be the series we prioritize recording and releasing first! And unlike a normal Choose Your Own Adventure Book, all paths lead to fun! There's no risk in making a mistake and getting yourself killed mid-video.

attributes.title: Choose our next series! Game 2: Satisfactory
attributes.description: It's Day 2 of Pilot Week and up next is Satisfactory! Jack, BK, Joe, and Matt have orders from Mr. Ficsit himself, to build a space elevator. Can the gang finish their tasks in time, or will they all get distracted by petting alien dogs and jumping on bouncy backs.

attributes.title: Choose our next series! Game 3: Sea Of Thieves
attributes.description: Welcome to Pilot Week: Choose Your Own Let's Play. To learn more, turn to below the description. | Join Matt, Michael, Joe, and Lindsay as they take on the high seas and set sail in search of the Shroudbreaker.  Will the new crew be able to tackle the waves or will they be sunk before their adventure even begins? | Choose Your Own Let's Play in Pilot Week! Whichever video winds up with the most views will be the series we prioritize recording and releasing first! And unlike a normal Choose Your Own Adventure Book, all paths lead to fun! There's no risk in making a mistake and getting yourself killed mid-video.

attributes.title: Choose our next series! Game 4: Remnant: From the Ashes
attributes.description: Welcome to Pilot Week: Choose Your Own Let's Play. To learn more, turn to below the description. | Day 4 of Pilot Week is here and Alfredo, BK, and Joe are diving into Remnant: From the Ashes! There's no risk in making a mistake and getting yourself killed mid-video.

attributes.title: Choose our next series! Game 5: 7 Days to Die
attributes.description: Welcome to Pilot Week: Choose Your Own Let's Play. To learn more, turn to below the description. | It's Day 5 of Pilot Week and up next is 7 Days to Die! Michael, Jack, BK, Trevor, and Matt return to the world from YDYD to see how they'll fare on Day 14. | Choose Your Own Let's Play in Pilot Week! Whichever video winds up with the most views will be the series we prioritize recording and releasing first! And unlike a normal Choose Your Own Adventure Book, all paths lead to fun! There's no risk of making a mistake and getting yourself killed mid-video.

attributes.title: I'm Stronger Than Your Basic Enemies! | My First Dark Souls Game #5
attributes.description: Majin Joe is back to continue his journey, slaying enemies and looking for more bosses to take down! He has defeated all who oppose him! With his Uchigatana in hand, he still pushes forward, so that he may finally hang up his loincloth... and maybe finally wash it.

attributes.title: Worst. Respawns. Ever. - Let's Play Halo 5 LASO (#5)
attributes.description: LASO ALARM! It's time to hunker down and get ready for LASO Part 5. Gavin, Michael, Alfredo, and Joe are back at it and attempting to do what feels to be damn near impossible. Grenades? Plenty. Downs? Several dozens. Yelling? So. Much. Of it.

attributes.title: Let’s Play Among Us VR
attributes.description: EMERGENCY MEETING! The gang is back in VR for some good ol’ Among Us with proxy chat! Will they work together to sus out the imposter in time, or immediately turn on each other and make wild accusations. I think we all know which one it’ll be..

attributes.title: Let's Play High on Life - The Next Rick and Morty
attributes.description: BK and Alfredo dive in the hilariously insane world of High on Life, as they fight with sentient weapons with crass senses of humor to avoid getting turned into drugs by the dangerous G3 Cartel and become the greatest and funniest bounty hunter in the galaxy.

attributes.title: Playing the NEW Wave 3 Maps! - Let's Play Mario Kart 8
attributes.description: Mario Kart 8 just released it's next batch of maps and we're here to give them a whirl. Ky, Lindsay, Michael, Matt, and BK are joined by a very special guest, Blizzb3ar from Squad Team Force where we check out the 8 new tracks as well as testing out the new Custom Items feature! You thought regular Mario Kart got chaotic? Wait until it's just Blue Shells and Bloopers.

attributes.title: 15 Hours in and We've Barely Scratched the Surface - Marvel's Midnight Suns
attributes.description: Jack and Alfredo take a look at Marvel's Midnight Suns. A deck-building strategy game with more extra content than we know what to do with!

attributes.title: We Become Criminals in Thief Simulator VR!
attributes.description: We’re back in VR! This week, Trevor, BK, and Alfredo break and enter in Thief Simulator VR. Maybe if playing video games doesn’t work out, the gang could give full time crime a try.

attributes.title: How To Lose Your Souls in 60 Seconds | My First Dark Souls Game #6
attributes.description: Majin Joe has been through quite a lot. He has been defeated by men with sticks, crabs, and a boss with sacks. He keeps losing souls by the thousands. Will Majin Joe ever not lose his souls? That seems very unlikely.

attributes.title: The Return of Al-cup-o and Mug-chael | Cuphead: The Delicious Last Course Part 1
attributes.description: Once upon a time, our heroes Alfredo "Al-cup-o" Diaz and Michael "Mug-chael" Jones beat the entirety of Cuphead in the most stress-inducing, raging week of their lives. Now, with the release of Cuphead: The Delicious Last Course, they make their triumphant return and begin to tackle the DLC bosses! Surely the skills gained months ago have stayed, and they will breeze through every boss, first try!
